https://doi.org/10.5067/MEaSUREs/GFSAD/G.Description: The Global Food Security-support Analysis Data (GFSAD) Cropland Extent 2015 Europe, Central Asia, Russia, Middle East product 30 m V001 dataset provides cropland extent data over Europe, Central Asia, Russia, and the Middle East for the year 2015.
